<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234177>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46 – 61. Males, gonostylus, dorsal and lateral views: 46, 47 — Sphecodes nippon; 48, 49 — S. pinguiculus Pérez; 50, 51 — S. puncticeps Thomson; 52, 53 — S. reticulatus Thomson; 54, 55 — S. rufiventris (Panzer); 56, 57 — S. scabricollis Wesmael; 58, 59 — S. schwarzi, sp. nov.; 60, 61 — S. spinulosus Hagens. Dark indicate thickened areas. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234177/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234178>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62 – 68. Males, head: 62 – 64 — frontal view; 65 – 68 — dorsal view; 62 — Sphecodes pinguiculus Pérez; 63 — S. schwarzi, sp. nov.; 64 — S. geoffrellus (Kirby); 65 — S. cristatus Hagens; 66 — S. nippon Meyer; 67 — S. reticulatus Thomson; 68 — S. longulus Hagens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234178/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234180>
    dc:description "FIGURES 72 – 76. Males: 72 – 75 — metasoma; 76 — hind tibia; 72 — Sphecodes alternatus Smith, T 4; 73 — S. reticulatus Thomson, T 4; 74 — S. kozlovi Astafurova & Proshchalykin; 75 — S. schwarzi sp. nov., T 1 – T 3; 76 — S. spinulosus Hagens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

